T02TD3278E:26b-1: tree lokya bi dza ya s'a dha nam /
T02TD3278E:26b-3: khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3278E:26b-4: sngar bshad pa'i cho gas nyi ma la yi ge h'um mthing nag las byung ba'i rje btsun khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba ste /
T02TD3278E:26b-5: sku mdog mthing nag zhal bzhi pa /
T02TD3278E:26b-7: zhal dang po khro bo sgeg pa dang ldan pa'o //
T02TD3278E:26b-8: g-yas pa ni drag rkan dang ldan pa'o //
T02TD3278E:26b-9: g-yon pa ni shin tu 'jigs su rung ba'o //
T02TD3278E:26b-10: rgyab ma ni dpa' bo'i nyams su ldan pa'o //
T02TD3278E:26b-11: rdo rje dang dril bu dang ldan pa'i phyag gnyis kyis ni thugs kar rdo rje h'um mdzad kyi phyag rgya 'dzin pa /
T02TD3278E:26b-12: g-yas pa'i phyag gsum gyis ni ral gri dang lcags kyu dang mda' bsnams pa'o //
T02TD3278E:26b-13: g-yon pa'i phyag gsum gyis ni gzhu dang /
T02TD3278E:26b-16: zhabs g-yon pa brkyang bskum gyis dbang phyug chen po'i mgo bo mnan pa /
T02TD3278E:26b-17: zhabs g-yas pa goo r'i nu ma gnyis kun nas mnan pa /
T02TD3278E:26b-18: sangs rgyas kyi phreng ba dang phreng ba la sogs pa rnam par bkra ba'i na bza' dang rgyan dang ldan par bdag nyid rnam par bsams la phyag rgya bcing bar bya ste /
T02TD3278E:26b-19: de la khu tshur gnyis kyi rgyab sbyar la mthe'u chung gnyis lu gu rgyud kyi rnam par sbyar bar byas pa'o //
T02TD3278E:26b-23: grihn'a pa ya grihn'a pa ya h'um /
T02TD3278E:26b-24: a'a na ya ho bha ga b'a na bi dy'a r'a dza h'um phat /
T02TD3278E:26b-25: khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba'i sgrub thabs so /
T02TD3278E:26b-27: // / aa bha ya las dge slong tshul khrims rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur ba'o /
